{"tid":782610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文化中心職員勸大媽離開指「遲早都取締」 歌迷：大家都係中國人！","createTime":"2018-08-17T01:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T03:17:09.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ca62010c3dbc38689565bb4ec0b1aa494db1c75a","tid":782610,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"文化中心職員勸大媽離開指「遲早都取締」 歌迷：大家都係中國人！"},{"pid":"3ddc414e72f2fc2deab373deb3c169c20cf1c974","tid":782610,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:25:45.000Z","msg":"天星碼頭再有大媽表演者被勸喻離開。十多名文化中心職員及約十名警察，於五號碼頭附近包圍正在唱歌的大媽，指有人投訴其表演聲量太大，希望大媽停止表演。<br />\n<br />\n數名職員及警察最初在附近觀察，不少觀眾邊聽歌邊打拍子，亦有人拿起手機直播表演。至大約十時，十多名文化中心職員列隊包圍表演者，勸喻表演者離開。文化中心職員指「我哋有紀錄(聲量)，你係違反咗&hellip;&hellip;你日日係咁都唔係辦法，我哋呢度遲早都要取締㗎喇」，並與表演者的「頭目」商談。<br />\n有聽眾就插嘴，「而家呢啲又唔係嘈，而家講理由，大家都係中國人嚟，而家係鬼佬呀？」至於表演者就指，自己與表演者唱歌聲量差不多，不明白自己為何被投訴。<br />\n經一輪糾纏後，表演者最終願收拾物品離去。"},{"pid":"25b3841119115310bb39a99cb77015c6c066d06e","tid":782610,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180816/large/1534431368_83aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180816%2Flarge%2F1534431368_83aa.jpg&h=aef500a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十多名尖沙咀文化中心職員及約十名警察，於五號碼頭附近包圍正在唱歌的大媽，指有人投訴其表演聲量太大，希望大媽停止表演。張柏基攝 (蘋果日報)"},{"pid":"4a881b39b7f6871b6e558733b7c9164dc7179bbb","tid":782610,"uid":7343,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:26:33.000Z","msg":"中你老母國人呀"},{"pid":"af5445a4c62eaf7247edaa76275d344631597c2c","tid":782610,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ba7caf778630f2ff8147eb89d91d01849b7c29","tid":782610,"uid":44171,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"大家都係中國人, 不如你班廢老送埋副身家畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cad0f302301bb51299402ae02900e8f85551ff0","tid":782610,"uid":152476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:30:55.000Z","msg":"難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"a0fe1ce97b20b1a9a68b61d69f3b5f22c7d20db1","tid":782610,"uid":27251,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"啲廢老仲係有白人高尚既觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143a4c76a05c09ed07b3569a0ab278ef53bc3d5c","tid":782610,"uid":40060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"同呢班廢中廢老講根本，冇文化就係冇文化，一日有佢哋喺度香港都只會繼續衰落去"},{"pid":"7c0dda9341a09bd4d03d2ec0d2627bd3f2479772","tid":782610,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0fe1ce97b20b1a9a68b61d69f3b5f22c7d20db1","tid":782610,"uid":27251,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"啲廢老仲係有白人高尚既觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:31:59.000Z","msg":"自曝其短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地思想既缺陷"},{"pid":"65dd5eb873916e77e680e134e80c6b179d23af5f","tid":782610,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:32:03.000Z","msg":"攞中國人名號厄飯食系列"},{"pid":"2fc8719f87997abe0bc58ca087228801138356a7","tid":782610,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:32:13.0